des:
If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : customer.connect@orientelectric.com 

Amazon Alexa and the Orient Smart home products work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light. 
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your Orient Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Orient Smart" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Orient account in our "Orient Smart" app;
(3). You need to have some Orient smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Orient Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Orient Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Orient Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Orient Smart", and you'll be navigated to Orient login page;
(9). Input your Orient account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:


“Alexa,discover my devices.”
"Alexa, turn on bedroom fan.”
“Alexa, turn off bedroom fan.”
“Alexa, set bedroom fan to 2.”

“Alexa,turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."

Currently this skill supports following products:
smart fan,
smart light,
